#!/usr/bin/env bash
set -euo pipefail

cat <<'HELP'
CESO AI Workflow Kit Help

Terminal commands:
  scripts/configure
      Add or update a local profile with guided setup.

  scripts/configure --help
      Show detailed configure/reset/remove-profile help.

  scripts/sync-and-commit
      Sync all configured sources, generate Codex files, install them, commit,
      and push.

  scripts/sync-and-commit --profile <name> "Commit message"
      Sync only one configured profile.

  scripts/sync-and-commit --list-profiles
      List configured profiles.

  scripts/sync-claude-to-codex
      Generate Codex files from the Claude-side files in this repo.

  scripts/install
      Install generated Codex files into ~/.codex.

  scripts/install-codex-wrapper
      Install the stable Codex startup wrapper into ~/.local/bin.

  scripts/doctor
      Check whether the local kit and Codex install are present.

Claude conversation commands:
  Update the CESO AI workflow kit.
      Claude should run scripts/sync-and-commit.

  Update the CESO AI workflow kit for <profile>.
      Claude should run scripts/sync-and-commit --profile <profile>.

  Add or change a project profile in the CESO AI workflow kit.
      Claude should run scripts/configure.

Codex conversation commands:
  Update the CESO AI workflow kit and verify what changed.
      Codex should pull, sync, install, then report git/sync/verification
      results from installed ~/.codex files.

  Update the CESO AI workflow kit for <profile> and verify what changed.
      Codex should refresh the kit and focus verification on that profile.

Important files:
  config.local.json
      Gitignored local source/profile config.

  config.example.json
      Committed template for local config.

  claude/
      Source-of-truth assistant files.

  codex/
      Generated files. Do not hand-edit.
HELP
